column2: SELECT TOP #   a.SPECOBJID AS AKARI_ID,   a.RA AS AKARI_RA,   a.DEC AS AKARI_DEC,	 	      gsl.specObjID AS sdssid1,   gsl.SpecObjID AS sdssid2,      gsl.nii_#_flux AS NII_#_FLUX,   gsl.sii_#_flux AS SII_#_FLUX,   gsl.oi_#_flux AS OI_#_FLUX,   gsl.oiii_#_flux AS OIII_#_FLUX,   gsl.h_alpha_flux AS H_ALPHA_FLUX,   gsl.h_beta_flux AS H_BETA_FLUX,      gsl.nii_#_flux_err AS NII_#_flux_err,   gsl.sii_#_flux_err AS SII_#_flux_err,   gsl.oi_#_flux_err AS OI_#_flux_err,   gsl.oiii_#_flux_err AS OIII_#_flux_err,   gsl.h_alpha_flux_err AS H_ALPHA_flux_err,   gsl.h_beta_flux_err AS H_BETA_flux_err,    n.distance AS angDist     into    mydb.test1   from    MyDB.sdss8 AS a       OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( a.RA, a.DEC, #) AS n    LEFT JOIN galSpecLine AS gsl ON gsl.SpecObjID = n.objid
